    Collection
    Collection.append(String key, Object value)
    Appends an item to the end of the item set with the given key.
    If there is no item set with the given key, a new one will be created.

    Adds or overwrites an item set to the Collection.
    Collection
    Collection.remove(String key)
    Removes the item set with the given key.
    If the key does not exist, this will be ignored.
    Collection
    Collection.remove(String key, int index)
    Remove a single item from the item set with the given key.
